vendor hub intergation API

if branch, what is the GST of the parent. 
 First validation will be PAN corresponds to given GST if  GST exists in input. Else fail 
 If request does not say branch{
   if GST is available{
      makes sure GST does not already exist
      AND  make sure that there is no entry  with  related PAN
   } else if GST not available AND PAN available {
      make sure PAN does not exists already
   } else if GST not available AND PAN not available AND account available {
     make sure the account is not already available
   }
} else if branch{
       makes sure GST does not already exist
      Create new vendor/partner as invoicing contact of type company with parent as vendor with GST reported as parent GST in the request API. 
}
